<div
    class="modal"
    tabindex="-1"
    role="dialog"
    id="assessment-selection-modal"
  >
  <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h1 class="modal-title display-header mx-4">
          LET'S GET STARTED!
        </h1>
        <button
          type="button"
          class="close"
          data-dismiss="modal"
          aria-label="Close"
        >
          <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="modal-body mx-4">
        <p>
          This tool will help you create Draft 0.1 of your NAPHS plan by utilizing your country assessment data (JEE or SPAR) and suggested actions from the Benchmarks.   
        </p>

        <p>
          When you finish, you’ll have a draft plan that can act as a jumping off point for further refinement, leading to accelerated progress for implementation and stepping up.
        </p>

        <p>
          The plans are comprised of actions based on the gap between the existing assessment score and your goal score.  
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>Create a plan by a recent assessment or by capacity areas:</strong>
        </p>

        <%= form_tag '/country_select', id: "assessment-select-menu",
          data: { target: "assessment-selection.form" } do %>
          <div class="input-group mb-4">
            <%= select_tag "country",
              options_from_collection_for_select(@countries, 'name', 'name'),
              class: "custom-select",
              data: { target: "assessment-selection.countrySelect",
                      action: "assessment-selection#selectCountry
                               assessment-selection#validateAndEnableNext"
                    }
            %>
          </div>
          <div class="input-group mb-4">
            <%= select_tag "assessment_type",
              options_from_collection_for_select([], 'assessment_type', 'assessment_type'),
              class: "custom-select",
              data: { target: "assessment-selection.assessmentTypeSelect",
                      action: "assessment-selection#validateAndEnableNext" } %>
          </div>
          <%= button_tag "Next",
            type: :button,
            class: "btn btn-primary w-100",
            disabled: true,
            data: { target: "assessment-selection.submitForm",
                    action: "assessment-selection#next",
                    current: "assessment-selection-modal",
                    next: "capacity-selection-modal" } %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
